	<h1 class="title">「这世界」2016 年总统竞选，硅谷大佬都站在了谁后面</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-26 12:11:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14005/medium/14005.jpeg?1440548089" alt="" />			
	</div>
